  "detailed_description": "NUVAVULT is a perspective altering puzzle game where 2D and 3D collide. What intially appears to be a classic 2D platformer soon transforms into something much... deeper.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou progress through several zones, each introducing a new way to alter and interact with the world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe 70+ puzzles are designed to reveal how the world works, without the need for explanation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe world is not as flat as it first appears.",
  "about_the_game": "NUVAVULT is a perspective altering puzzle game where 2D and 3D collide. What intially appears to be a classic 2D platformer soon transforms into something much... deeper.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou progress through several zones, each introducing a new way to alter and interact with the world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe 70+ puzzles are designed to reveal how the world works, without the need for explanation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe world is not as flat as it first appears.",
